{"id":"summaries/2018-11-08-1928-papi-said-he-would-see-yermers-11-7-18","title":"1928 — Papi said he would see Yermers 11-7-18","type":"summaries","html":"<p>Title-only ledger note from teen Yahir — <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">dad yahir</a> (\"Papi\") said he would see \"Yermers\" (Yahir) on 11-7-18; logged in the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/dad-death-premonitions\">dad death premonitions</a> arc as another timestamped fragment.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">dad yahir</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/dad-death-premonitions\">dad death premonitions</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/grants-pass-teen-era\">grants pass teen era</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/dad-death-premonitions","label":"Dad Death Premonitions"},{"id":"entities/dad-yahir","label":"Dad Yahir"},{"id":"concepts/grants-pass-teen-era","label":"Grants Pass Teen Era"}]}
